## Prompt-building Logic (Reference)

| Scenario | Output |
|---|---|
| Single user, no system | `<s>[INST] {user1} [/INST]` |
| Single user, with system | `<s>[INST] {system}\n{user1} [/INST]` |
| Multi-turn, with system | `<s>[INST] {system}\n{user1} [/INST] {asst1}</s>[INST] {user2} [/INST]` |
| Multi-turn, no system | `<s>[INST] {user1} [/INST] {asst1}</s>[INST] {user2} [/INST]` |

Key details:
- `<s>` only at the very start (before the first `[INST]`)
- Space between `[/INST]` and assistant content: ` {content}</s>`
- No space before `[INST]` on subsequent user turns

